entries.s_f1e05b2b: Col. Talnin here will not be of use to you unless you're involved with space flight.
entries.s_e6fab5c8: Look, I really don't care who you are or why you're here. I just want my money from Col. Talnin, and then I'm gone.
entries.s_a3171132: Why does he owe you money?
entries.s_7d382d7: You have questions, then ask 'Mr. Travel Vouchers' here. He's the bigshot Imperial officer. Just make sure he never owes you money.
entries.s_5ff8baab: I was wondering if you could answer some questions?
entries.s_5bb4c9f9: Oh sorry. Could you answer some other questions?
entries.s_2b9bb31e: Whoa there! That's not really the kind of question you just up and ask someone. I don't talk about the details of a client's gambling debt to random people. So just let it go.
